&lt;li&gt;Vin: 3 to 5VDC (always use 3.3v with your &lt;a href="/data-acquisition-module"&gt;Nwazet DAQ module&lt;/a&gt;)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Logic: 3 to 5V compliant&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Pressure sensing range: 300-1100 hPa (9000m to -500m above sea level)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Up to 0.03hPa / 0.25m resolution&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;-40 to +85°C operational range, +-2°C temperature accuracy&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;

